text: Twann-Tüscherz () is a municipality of the administrative district of Biel/Bienne in the canton of Bern in Switzerland. On 1 January 2010, the former municipalities of Twann and Tüscherz-Alfermée merged into the new municipality of Twann-Tüscherz. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:2010 establishments in Switzerland Category:Municipalities in Biel/Bienne
